{{ collector_contracts_block }}{{ environment_block }}## Dataset Structure

Minari-compatible flat table format. Use `minari-export` for native [Minari](https://minari.farama.org/) HDF5 format.

Each trajectory has N step rows plus one final observation row (N+1 pattern).
The final observation is the state after the last step. It has a null action and
null values for rewards/terminations/truncations/infos. `collector_terminated=true`
on that row means collection stopped before a provider termination or truncation;
the provider transition values remain unchanged.

